<div class="modal fade" id="deliverymodal" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="myModalLabel">
    <div class="modal-dialog" role="document">
        <div class="modal-content">
            <div class="modal-header">
                <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"><span aria-hidden="true">&times;</span></button>
                <h4 class="modal-title" id="myModalLabel"><strong>Delivery Area  </strong></h4>
            </div>
            <div class="modal-body">

                <img src="~/Content/Images/mymap.png" style="width:100%" />
            </div>
            <div class="modal-footer">
                <button type="button" class="btn btn-default" data-dismiss="modal">Close</button>

            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>


<!--modal 1 for step 2-->

<div class="modal fade" id="step2infomodal" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="myModalLabel">
    <div class="modal-dialog" role="document">
        <div class="modal-content">
            <div class="modal-header">
                <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"><span aria-hidden="true">&times;</span></button>
                <h4 class="modal-title" id="myModalLabel"> <strong> Membership Info </strong></h4>
            </div>
            <div class="modal-body">
                <ul>
                    <li> New memberships take 3 business days to process before delivery begins on 4th business day</li>
                    <li> Each membership level requires two months minimum subscription</li>
                    <li> All memberships are paid auto-pay on the 7th of each month</li>
                    <li>
                        If member will be travelling or away from home during a period of 3 or more days:
                        <ul>
                            <li> member can withold delivery for up to 10 days max at which time membership can be suspended</li>
                            <li> the witheld time can be credited to member's account balance for the following payment cycle  </li>
                            <li> 5 days prior notice is required via email with "from" and "to" dates member will be away</li>
                        </ul>
                    </li>
                    <li> Memberships renew monthly automatically and require 30 days notice via email to cancel subscription</li>
                    <li> Membership upgrades will process for the following month</li>
                    <li>
                        There is no fee for joining or cancelling, but keep in mind if you cancel mid-month, you will be charged for <br />
                        the following month's subscription whether you choose to keep the juices or not.
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="modal-footer">
                <button type="button" class="btn btn-default" data-dismiss="modal">Close</button>

            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

